{% set name = "Represent" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}

source:

  sha256: 293dfec8b2e9e2150a21a49bfec2cd009ecb600c8c04f9186d2ad222c3cef78a 

build:
 number: 4
 script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv"

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}
  host:
    - python
    - pip
    - six >=1.8.0
  run:
    - python
    - six >=1.8.0

test:

    - represent

  dev_url: https://github.com/RazerM/represent
